# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:14
translate spanish mari13_8ff999a9:

    # "My phone starts buzzing in my pocket."
    "Mi teléfono empieza a vibrar en mi bolsillo."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:19
translate spanish mari13_cc03b1d7:

    # fr "Hey, [pcname]. I had a question for you. Do you know anything about cars?"
    fr "Hola, [pcname]. Tengo una pregunta para ti. ¿Sabes algo de coches?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:20
translate spanish mari13_988170b5:

    # pc "Just a little, why?"
    pc "Solo un poco, ¿por qué?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:22
translate spanish mari13_0aae16d6:

    # fr "Well, I have my dad's old truck out in the barn, and it's not running right now."
    fr "Bueno, tengo la vieja camioneta de mi padre en el granero y ahora mismo no funciona."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:23
translate spanish mari13_180b4647:

    # fr "I thought maybe if I could get it running again, I could try to learn how to drive."
    fr "Pensé que si conseguía que volviera a funcionar, podría intentar aprender a conducir."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:24
translate spanish mari13_1eb798c6:

    # pc "Is that what you want? I thought you were afraid of cars."
    pc "¿Es eso lo que quieres? Creía que le tenías miedo a los coches."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:26
translate spanish mari13_5a2e5dff:

    # fr "I am... but I think I need to move forward. My assistant veterinary position is in Whiterock, so I'm going to have to drive back and forth."
    fr "Lo tengo... pero creo que necesito seguir adelante. Mi puesto de asistente veterinaria está en Whiterock, así que voy a tener que conducir de ida y vuelta."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:27
translate spanish mari13_ed288529:

    # fr "I don't want to have to rely on somebody else to take me all the time."
    fr "No quiero tener que depender de que alguien me lleve todo el tiempo."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:28
translate spanish mari13_d64bc11a:

    # pc "That makes sense."
    pc "Tiene sentido."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:30
translate spanish mari13_fa47ee6f:

    # fr "So, do you think you could come look at my truck and see if you can figure out what's wrong with it?"
    fr "Entonces, ¿crees que podrías venir a echarle un vistazo a mi camioneta y ver si averiguas qué le pasa?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:31
translate spanish mari13_47996b5f:

    # pc "Sure, I'll come look."
    pc "Claro, iré a echarle un vistazo."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:33
translate spanish mari13_4b7d8262:

    # fr "Thanks, [pcname]. See you in a little while."
    fr "Gracias, [pcname]. Nos vemos en un rato."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:36
translate spanish mari13_0a3a1d94:

    # "I hang up and start driving out to Mari's farm."
    "Cuelgo y empiezo a conducir hacia la granja de Mari."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:39
translate spanish mari13_86dfe7f8:

    # "When I get to Mari's house, we go out to the barn together and I pop the hood on the truck."
    "Cuando llego a la casa de Mari, salimos juntas al granero y levanto el capó de la camioneta."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:40
translate spanish mari13_14d2a400:

    # fr "Do you think you can fix it?"
    fr "¿Crees que podrás arreglarla?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:41
translate spanish mari13_1638d0b9:

    # pc "I can try. I'm sure the battery is dead, first of all. Let's take that out and get it charged."
    pc "Puedo intentarlo. Para empezar, estoy seguro de que la batería está agotada. Vamos a sacarla y a cargarla."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:42
translate spanish mari13_118245c8:

    # pc "Do you have wrenches or a socket set or anything?"
    pc "¿Tienes llaves inglesas, un juego de llaves de vaso o algo así?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:43
translate spanish mari13_981633b9:

    # fr "I'm sure I do. There's a bunch of Dad's tools over here. I'll show you."
    fr "Seguro que sí. Por aquí hay un montón de herramientas de papá. Te las enseño."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:46
translate spanish mari13_9f27c930:

    # "Using her dad's old tools, I take the battery out of the truck and we drive it to a nearby autoparts store."
    "Con las viejas herramientas de su padre, saco la batería de la camioneta y nos dirigimos a una tienda de recambios cercana."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:47
translate spanish mari13_48f63bf1:

    # "It ends up being bad, so Mari buys a new one, and we return to the truck once again."
    "Al final resulta que está estropeada, así que Mari compra una nueva y volvemos a la camioneta."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:50
translate spanish mari13_25ce6fc4:

    # pc "Well, now it's getting power, but it's not turning over."
    pc "Bueno, ahora recibe corriente, pero no arranca."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:51
translate spanish mari13_3173e3d2:

    # fr "What do you think it is? The pistons?"
    fr "¿Qué crees que es? ¿Los pistones?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:52
translate spanish mari13_00123606:

    # pc "What makes you say that?"
    pc "¿Por qué lo dices?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:53
translate spanish mari13_53ea273a:

    # fr "I don't know. It's just a car term I've heard before."
    fr "No lo sé. Es solo un término de coches que he oído antes."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:54
translate spanish mari13_d12b1362:

    # fr "I don't know anything about cars."
    fr "No sé nada de coches."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:55
translate spanish mari13_95134570:

    # pc "I'm not really sure what's causing it not to start at this point."
    pc "No estoy muy seguro de qué está provocando que no arranque en este momento."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:60
translate spanish mari13_f47dff33:

    # "WARNING!"
    "¡ADVERTENCIA!"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:61
translate spanish mari13_66b8cb1f:

    # rj "Sorry to interrupt, but if you continue right now, you will miss a scene that you might want to see!"
    rj "Siento interrumpir, pero si sigues ahora mismo, ¡te perderás una escena que quizá te interese ver!"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:63
translate spanish mari13_793e8063:

    # rj "You can continue with this scene right now, but you will miss a threesome scene with Reba and Mari."
    rj "Puedes continuar con esta escena ahora mismo, pero te perderás una escena de trío con Reba y Mari."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:64
translate spanish mari13_908919a8:

    # rj "To get the threesome scene you need to have had sex with Reba before inviting her over to fix Mari's truck."
    rj "Para ver la escena del trío, tienes que haber tenido sexo con Reba antes de invitarla a arreglar la camioneta de Mari."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:65
translate spanish mari13_0323a8c0:

    # rj "Are you sure you want to continue and miss the Mari/Reba threesome?"
    rj "¿Estás seguro de que quieres continuar y perderte el trío de Mari y Reba?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:69
translate spanish mari13_380064ab:

    # rj "Okay then! No complaining online that you missed it!"
    rj "¡De acuerdo, entonces! ¡No te quejes en Internet de que te lo has perdido!"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:71
translate spanish mari13_e431e7a9:

    # rj "I'll leave and let you get back to the game now! Have fun!"
    rj "¡Me voy a ir para que puedas volver al juego! ¡Diviértete!"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:74
translate spanish mari13_0d0f23dd:

    # pc "But I know somebody who might be able to help."
    pc "Pero conozco a alguien que podría ayudarte."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:76
translate spanish mari13_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/mari_ohcool1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_ohcool1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:77
